headline: A Few Years From Now, You'll Wish You Bought This Undervalued Stock
summary: Hormel Foods (NYSE: HRL) is a Dividend King offering a historically high 3.6% dividend yield.  It appears to be on the sale rack right now, and a few years from now, long-term dividend investors will probably wish they had bought it.  In theory, that should mean they make decisions that are in the best long-term interests of their investors.
